channel.title: Kanye West's VMA Interruption Sparks Latest Internet Meme
channel.description:
[IMG]http://www2.pictures.zimbio.com/mp/gaM052ri-9Ol.jpg[/img]
Kanye West's interruption of Taylor Swift's VMA acceptance speech has sparked the latest Internet meme as pictures crop up depicting the pop star interrupting people. On Sunday, Kanye West jumped on stage to interrupt Taylor by saying, "Yo Taylor, I'm really happy for you, I'm gonna let you finish, but Beyonce had one of the best videos of all time."
Here's the actual video of what happened - [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1z8gCZ7zpsQ&feature=related]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1z8gCZ7zpsQ&feature=related[/url]
